KW  - FT-SE100 Index
AB  - The paper performs an empirical estimation of time-varying volatility using OLS regression. Error Components, and Dummy Variable models, by regressing the implied volatility on time to maturity, the strike price and a dummy. Both the daily OLS equations and the panel data model provide more accurate estimates of Black and Scholes option prices than the bench-mark standard deviation of log returns. FT-SE 100 Index European options are used for empirical analysis.
